/**
 * Custom hook to subscribe to field change and isolate re-rendering at the component level.
 *
 * @remarks
 *
 * [API](https://react-hook-form.com/api/usewatch) • [Demo](https://codesandbox.io/s/react-hook-form-v7-ts-usewatch-h9i5e)
 *
 * @example
